<h2>Subcommand: <code>pattern</code></h2>
<h3>Usage</h3>
<pre class='example'>
north pattern
hand {AJ32 A5 JTxx xxx} pattern
</pre>
<h3>Summary</h3>
Returns a sorted list of the suit lengths, starting with the longest.
For example, the second command above would return the list:
<pre class='example'>
