<a name="full_deal"></a>
<h2>Command: <code>full_deal</code></h2>
<table cellpadding=5 style="width: 100%">
<tr valign=top><td style="width: 65%">
<h3>Usage</h3>
<pre class='example'>
   set deal [full_deal]
</pre>
<p>This simple utility command returns the deal as a list of hands in the order of north, east, south, and west.  Suitable for passing into <a href="#ddscmd"><code>dds</code></a> with the <code>-diagram</code> flag, or remembering a deal after the end of the loop.
</td>
